        Me time day – Let the relaxing begin

      %p
        The night before I put fresh bedding on, so I wake up all relaxed and ready to enjoy my day.
        I like to start with a little lie in to ensure that I wake nicely recharged and relaxed and ready for my me time-day to begin.
        Next, I have a delicious breakfast of some of my favorite things and make sure it has a few healthy aspects to add to my well-being.
        Feel free to turn it into breakfast in bed if you want, it’s your day remember, just do as you please and definitely don’t get dressed if you don’t want to.
        The day is all about doing exactly what you want and when you want and doing it all in your own time.
        After a nice cup of tea, I like to pick a couple of favorite things to do and loosely plan them into my day.
        Today I am having a bit of a movie day and a nice hot bath a little later on.
        I also choose to have a little nap before lunch. 

