      %p
        Relaxing is hard work, especially if you are used to being on the go all the time, and it inevitable that you are going to need nourishment at some point.
        Make sure you have some tasty and easy to prepare lunch ideas to keep you happy and to be able to continue the feel good factor of your day.
        I love to have a late brunch and am happy to do the little prep it requires, but feel free to plan your snack in any way you want.
        The key here is not to spend too much time preparing your lunch, to have what you would really love and to enjoy it thoroughly.
        Obviously after your lunch you will need to take it slow, so you want a nice easy afternoon activity to help you digest.
        It’s at this point I either watch a favourite film or read a book, but I have been known to take a little couch nap and allow my food to digest real slow.
