        Remember you are catching up and checking in with yourself so pick something that you love to waste time doing, even if its absolutely nothing,
        just go ahead and do it.
        The idea is to enjoy the moment and the time to be by yourself for a while.
        Read that book you have always been meaning to.
        Watch your favourite film again, because there will be no interruptions, listen to some of your favourite music,
        just make sure it’s more on the relaxing side than the dance floor carnage side. 

