      %h3 
        Evening time – reflect and be sure

      %p
        Now you have had time to relax and reflect on your plans for the coming year,
        it is time to take another look at that list and see if your new goals still resonate with you and what you really want to achieve.
        Tomorrow is when you can start making plans to achieve all that is on your list, but today you should concentrate on making sure that they are things you really want.
        Try to think about what they will really bring to your life and if it is still the right thing for you.
        The key is to make your list about the things that will really mean something and make a difference.
        There is no point picking things that look great, but turn out to be not what you thought they would be.
        Choose the right plans now and you will achieve more and enjoy the outcome at the end too.
        I like to sit down with a nice dinner and a glass of wine and really think about what goals I have planned and how I planned to achieve them.

